snippet.title: Open Sails At The Golden Isles
snippet.description: Open Sails At The Golden Isles Adventure puzzle. You must guide your ship through the isle maze to succeed.

snippet.title: Home Sheep Home 2: Lost In London
snippet.description: Home Sheep Home 2: Lost In London Adventure game that requires teamwork of 3 sheep to get to the exit of each level.

snippet.title: Last Mars Tower
snippet.description: Last Mars Tower Strategy game. you operate the last defensive tower on Mars. Upgrade and conquer!

snippet.title: Free The Prince
snippet.description: Free The Prince Adventure puzzle. Try to save the prince using your puzzle skills to solve each platform puzzle.

snippet.title: Flippin' Dead
snippet.description: Flippin' Dead Arcade game. Set the highscore avoiding zombies and opening crates as long as you manage.

snippet.title: Go Go Goblin
snippet.description: Go Go Goblin Launch the goblin as far as possible. Take as much coins as you can for better upgrades.

snippet.title: Elevator Breakout
snippet.description: Elevator Breakout Shooting game. Get in the elevator and survive as long as you can shooting all sorts of robots.

snippet.title: Pixel Toilet
snippet.description: Pixel Toilet Arcade game. Make sure the dude on the toilet reaches the end of the level by launching him.

snippet.title: The Mechanicer
snippet.description: The Mechanicer Platform puzzle. Get the robot to the exit of each stage pulling switches, moving stuff and more.

snippet.title: Shop Empire 2
snippet.description: Shop Empire 2 Management game. Build a mall with all sorts of shops and hire staff to manage the building.
